What you need to know:

Kenya men's and women's teams failed to travel on Saturday to Ghana as scheduled after the Sports Fund board allegedly failed to have a session last Friday to approve the teams' budgetChances are high that the women's team will miss their opening fixture against Zambia should AHF fail to reschedule the tie or miss out on the event altogether should the Sports Fund fail to approve the budget on MondayThe women's team, who are in Pool 'B' were to start off their campaign against Zambia on Monday, play Ghana the following day before wrapping up their group matches against Nigeria on Thursday